title: Open Enrollment starts Wednesday October 12, 2015 (Vanderbilt University)
text: ( Source : Vanderbilt University ) Oct. 12, 2015 , 7:34 AM (iStockphoto) Open Enrollment for 2016 benefits starts Wednesday, Oct. 14 . Are you ready ? As a reminder, Open Enrollment is your annual opportunity to update or choose the benefit
